posting_body: ['PROP # 01K71', 'MIAMI: 3/2.5', 'Largest model of 3/2/1 in this lake complex with community pool.', '24 Hr. security & guard gated.', 'All bedrooms upstairs, full-size washer & dryer on main floor.', 'Ceramic & wood floors.', 'Corner unit with large yard & gazebo.', "The unit faces South, no direct sun -- it's nice and cool.", 'Great location, very close to 117 Ave & 152 St. exit from Turnpike.', 'Available Aug. 1.', 'Tenants must be approved by association first.', 'Each adult must submit application to association, with $150.00 fee each, unless married.', "Landlord requires credit report, 2 months security, one of which is required by the association, plus first month's rent.", "Tenant must give 60 days' notice prior to moving out.", 'Deposits will not be used as rent at any time.', 'Pets OK (HOA limit is 2 pets per unit, <30 lbs.).', 'On combination lock.', 'Read Less', 'Rent 1 Sale 1 Kendall', "Bad credit, no credit, come in we'll help you.", '*****', 'Se habla español *****', 'Interested in a property:', 'Call/Text-', 'show contact info', "786'+'7O8'+'2475", 'Call-', 'show contact info', "3O5'+'982'+'8O15", '**R1S1 -Kendall posts properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to current high rental demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, canceled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed**', 'T a g s:', '- Kendall', '- Fontainebleau', '- West Fontainebleau', '- Dadeland']
